Useful console procedures and functions for PCQ-Pascal
------------------------------------------------------
Based on the Andreas Tetzl's work I added, changed and
reworked some procedures and functions which allows
simple controlling of cursor positioning as well as
getting a single key without displaying it and something
more.

For further informations take a look at the source codes.

